notes: New 7th wicket partnership record v Zimbabwe, previous was 66
New 7th wicket partnership record for South Africa, previous was 76
50 partnership between Whittall/A Flower off 75 balls, 65 minutes
New 7th wicket partnership record v South Africa, previous was 63
New 7th wicket partnership record for Zimbabwe, previous was 81

milestones.description: Grant Flower has broken the record for most ducks (10) in ODIs for ZIM, going past Andy Flower's 9
Kallis and Klusener's 82-run partnership is SA's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 76 between Hansie Cronje and McMillan
Andy Flower and Guy Whittall's 91-run partnership is ZIM's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 81 between Campbell and Andy Whittall
